text: Nicki Minaj Shares Sweet Note to Blue Ivy Carter: 'You Are Going to Make an Amazing Big Sister' by Latifah Muhammad 10:09   Nicki Minaj Shares Sweet Note to Blue Ivy Carter: 'You Are Going to Make an Amazing Big Sister' Nicki Minaj is gushing over Blue Ivy Carter! The 34-year-old rapper sent a sweet sisterly message to Beyonce and Jay Z's daughter on Instagram on Thursday, in honor of the family's pregnancy news . Nicki Minaj's Beverly Hills Mansion Burglarized, $175,000 in Jewelry and Other Property Stolen "This beautiful little lady bug is so smart & special," Minaj wrote on Thursday, one day after it was revealed that Beyonce is expecting twins. "You guys have no idea! So Dear Blue, you are going to make an AMAZING big sister. Love always, Nicki" A photo posted by Nicki Minaj (@nickiminaj) on Feb 2, 2017 at 11:20am PST WATCH: Nicki Minaj and Drake Are Friends Again, Have a Young Money Reunion After Meek Mill Breakup Minaj is one of many celebs and fans that flooded the internet with posts celebrating Beyonce's pregnancy. Despite carrying twins, Queen Bey doesn't plan to slow down just yet. ET can confirm that the "Formation"singer will take the stage at the GRAMMY Awards in Los Angeles next Sunday. See more below.
